00:20:22,728 --> 00:20:24,395
-Couldn't help
it's not an answer!

516
00:20:24,428 --> 00:20:25,561
-What about Ouka and Shusui?

517
00:20:25,595 --> 00:20:27,128
Do you know if
they're all right?

518
00:20:27,161 --> 00:20:28,061
-They're OK.

519
00:20:28,095 --> 00:20:29,295
They don't seem to
be very shocked.

520
00:20:29,328 --> 00:20:31,161
In fact, they seem very normal.

521
00:20:31,195 --> 00:20:32,561
TOKIKO (VOICEOVER): Very normal?

522
00:20:32,595 --> 00:20:34,928
After being attacked by two
monstrous looking things

523
00:20:34,961 --> 00:20:37,928
and witnessing the Buso
Renkin with their own eyes?

524
00:20:37,961 --> 00:20:39,828
Behind you, KazukI!

525
00:20:39,861 --> 00:20:42,528
-First I'll be taking your life!

526
00:20:42,561 --> 00:20:45,495
[shout]

527
00:20:49,995 --> 00:20:52,195
KAZUKI (VOICEOVER): This
Homunculus is very strong.

528
00:20:52,228 --> 00:20:54,528
But I'm also a little
stronger than before.

529
00:20:54,561 --> 00:20:57,495
[shout]

530
00:20:57,528 --> 00:20:58,961
-Just get out of the way, Shi!

531
00:20:58,995 --> 00:21:01,261
Your Rain of Blows technique
is annoying to watch.

532
00:21:01,295 --> 00:21:05,461
It's better just to take him
out with one good, solid punch!

533
00:21:05,495 --> 00:21:07,661
[shout]

534
00:21:07,695 --> 00:21:09,795
TOKIKO (VOICEOVER): His
fighting style has changed.

535
00:21:09,828 --> 00:21:11,728
What were once
mainly charge attacks

536
00:21:11,761 --> 00:21:14,395
is now a skillful lance
control in response

537
00:21:14,428 --> 00:21:15,761
to the enemy's movement.

538
00:21:15,795 --> 00:21:18,528
The experience he's
gained in actual battle,

539
00:21:18,561 --> 00:21:20,795
in addition to his special
training with the Warrior

540
00:21:20,828 --> 00:21:23,461
Chief, the sparring
with Shisui Hayasaka,

541
00:21:23,495 --> 00:21:26,028
and his will to become
stronger have all

542
00:21:26,061 --> 00:21:27,995
come together to become one.

543
00:21:28,028 --> 00:21:31,728
-Kid, don't you be
getting carried away!

544
00:21:31,761 --> 00:21:33,028
-What?

545
00:21:33,061 --> 00:21:34,128
-This wound?

546
00:21:34,161 --> 00:21:37,461
Could it have been
inflicted from that time?

547
00:21:37,495 --> 00:21:39,895
The mission's a
complete disaster!

548
00:21:39,928 --> 00:21:41,828
-I won't let you get away!

549
00:21:45,728 --> 00:21:48,661
[scream]

550
00:21:48,695 --> 00:21:49,161
-Tokiko!

551
00:21:52,128 --> 00:21:53,661
-Kazuki's opponent
was just killed

552
00:21:53,695 --> 00:21:55,195
from an attack made
by a Buso Renkin.

553
00:21:57,695 --> 00:21:59,795
Two different types
of Buso Renkin.

554
00:21:59,828 --> 00:22:02,428
It seems the real enemy
is a different duo.

555
00:22:02,461 --> 00:22:04,395
-I'm sorry I messed up.

556
00:22:04,428 --> 00:22:05,361
-It's OK.

557
00:22:05,395 --> 00:22:07,995
Now we've seen
their Buso Renkin.

558
00:22:08,028 --> 00:22:10,861
Neither of them
is a match for me.

559
00:22:10,895 --> 00:22:13,428
-The Hayasaka twins
are the enemy.

560
00:22:13,461 --> 00:22:15,328
The LXE.

561
00:22:15,361 --> 00:22:15,828
Homunculi.

562
00:22:23,606 --> 00:22:27,006
[theme music]

563
00:23:54,601 --> 00:23:57,201
TOKIKO: It slices at an
abnormal speed and sharpness,

564
00:23:57,234 --> 00:23:59,934
and even Kazuki's energy
attacks have no effect.

565
00:23:59,967 --> 00:24:04,167
Shisui Hayasaka, just what sort
of Buso Renkin do you have?

566
00:24:04,201 --> 00:24:06,934
Next episode, It Seems
We're Well Matched.

567
00:24:06,967 --> 00:24:10,467
I'll splatter your guts!

